{"type": "article", "id": 7141, "title": "Paper lamp 简易纸灯", "description": "", "date": "2015-03-06T07:23:17Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 6, "image": "img/article/article_show/2016060523441527L9RS5AgQBnHrqb.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t近几年纸灯也火得一塌糊涂，之前我们介绍过<a href=\"http://qdaily.com/display/articles/6425.html\" target=\"_blank\">东京设计事务所 YOY 做的贴在墙壁上面的纸灯</a>，今天这个和他们做的纸灯有异曲同工之妙。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t法国设计事务所 Ligne Roset Réaumur 推出的这一款纸灯采用的是一种新型材料，这种非织造的透光材料既防撕裂又防燃烧。上面开一个小孔，打开后可以直接套在灯泡上就可以使用了。纸张外观印有条纹或格子图案，看上去非常时髦又现代化。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t</p>\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052344138T2sy6Eic5Rl3ktw.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:696px;\" data-ratio=\"1.28333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n\t</p>\r\n\t<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052344142lkxshfrCM5WVS3Y.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:696px;\" data-ratio=\"1.18\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n\t</p>\r\n\n\n"}